What is the output of this code?
x <- 10
if (x > 5) {
  print('yes')
} else {
  print('no')
}

How many times will this loop run?
for (i in 1:3) {
  print(i)
}

What is the output of this code?
for (i in 1:4) {
  if (i == 3) next
  print(i)
}

What does the following code print?
x <- 5
while (x > 0) {
  print(x)
  x <- x - 2
}

How many times is 'Hello' printed?
for (i in 1:3) {
  for (j in 1:2) {
    print('Hello')
  }
}

What is the value of x after this loop?
x <- 0
for (i in 1:4) {
  x <- x + i
}

